listener = Listener()
stream = [line for event in events for line in event]
listener.handle_stream_(stream)
assert listener.updates == [{'foo': 'bar'}]
assert listener.notifications == [{'foo': 'bar'}]
assert listener.deletes == [123]
assert listener.heartbeats == 2
pytest.mark.parametrize('events', itertools.permutations([['event: update',
    'data: {"foo": "bar"}', ''], ['event: notification',
    'data: {"foo": "bar"}', ''], ['event: delete', 'data: 123', ''], [
    ':toot toot'], [':beep beep']]))
